11) Recommended Endpoint Set (MVP)

Auth:
	•	POST /auth/login
	•	POST /auth/select-tenant (for multi-tenant users)
	•	POST /auth/refresh (rotation enabled)
	•	POST /auth/logout
	•	POST /auth/switch-tenant

Invites:
	•	POST /tenants/{tenantId}/staff/invite (admin-only)
	•	POST /auth/invites/accept

Password:
	•	POST /auth/password/forgot
	•	POST /auth/password/reset

⸻

12) Operational Notes

12.1 Token hashing

Always store hashes for:
	•	refresh tokens
	•	invite tokens
	•	reset tokens

Never store raw tokens.

12.2 Audit logging (recommended)

Log:
	•	invite created/accepted
	•	membership role changes
	•	membership disabled/enabled
	•	password resets
	•	refresh reuse detection triggers

