13) Final Locked Decisions Summary
	•	Users can join multiple tenants via memberships
	•	Access/refresh tokens are tenant-scoped (one tenant per session token)
	•	Invite-by-link and reset-by-link are supported
	•	Access TTL: 15 minutes
	•	Refresh TTL: 14 hours
	•	Refresh rotation enabled
	•	Membership disabled → immediate access denial
	•	Refresh token reuse after rotation → revoke tenant token family and force re-login